programme.title: PL Stories: Reggae Rhythms in the Premier League
programme.desc: Reggae Rhythms in the Premier League explores the powerful connection between Jamaica and the world’s most-watched football league, showcasing how the island’s culture, music, and style have influenced the Premier League. We feature iconic Jamaican players who have left their mark, while also diving into the impact of reggae music, fashion, and fan culture on the game. Through exclusive interviews and untold stories, we see how Jamaican heritage has shaped both football and broader global culture, from the pitch to the streets.(n)
